HEADWORD: Omdurman
<hw>Omdurman</hw> <pos>prop. n.</pos> <def>A battle (1898) in which an
Anglo-Egyptian army under <person>Lord Kitchener</person> defeated the
Sudanese.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> battle of Omdurman.</syn>⟦br⟧
